# HTML for NLP

## Installation

```bash
pip install git+https://github.com/druskacik/html_for_nlp
```

## Usage

```python

import requests
from html_for_nlp import HTMLDocument

r = requests.get('https://google.com')

doc = HTMLDocument(r.content)

print(doc.full_text)
```

